'''Steve Sauers''' is an [[Industrial Light & Magic]] employee. He was the digital model development and construction artist on [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']]<ref name="AOTC">{{Film|II}}</ref> and a digital model viewpaint and simulation artist for [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']].<ref name="ROTS">{{Film|III}}</ref>

